        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Constitution education Is Valuable In Community Schools Act of 2021 or the CIVICS Act of </b><strong>2021</strong></p> <p>This bill requires national activities supported by American History and Civics Education grants to include programs that educate students about the history and principles of the Constitution, including the Bill of Rights. </p>]]>
        </text>
